{"word":"καταλάμπω","slug":"καταλάμπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταλάμπω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-λάμψω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to shine upon</i> or <i>over</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <el>κ. τοὺς στενωπούς</el> <i>to light them</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to shine</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}